From 01cccf322fc607efdd6e7dd1f7e0d831df83cda1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: PurHur <PurHur@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 09:15:51 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Enable chunked GDN prefill on gfx1151 with L2 fusion.

Use CS=32 and global state scratch on RDNA3.5, add in-place L2 normalize
before chunked prefill, and lower the default chunk threshold to 16 tokens.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
---
